  "handbookContacts": "<p>Jefferson High School is one of five comprehensive high schools in the <strong>Jefferson Union High School District (JUHSD)</strong>, serving communities across northern San Mateo County.</p><h3>School Links</h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://jhs.juhsd.net\" target=\"_blank\">Jefferson High School Website</a></li><li><a href=\"https://jhs.juhsd.net/our-school/administration\" target=\"_blank\">JHS Administration Team</a></li><li><a href=\"https://jhs.juhsd.net/our-school/staff-directory\" target=\"_blank\">JHS Staff Directory</a></li></ul><h3>District Links</h3><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.juhsd.net/about-us/administration\" target=\"_blank\">JUHSD District Administration</a></li><li><a href=\"https://www.juhsd.net/about-us/board-of-trustees\" target=\"_blank\">JUHSD Governing Board</a></li></ul><h3>Contact Jefferson High School</h3><table><thead><tr><th>Department</th><th>Phone</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Main Office</td><td><a href=\"tel:+16505507700\">(650) 550-7700</a></td></tr></tbody></table>",
  "handbookBellSchedule": "<p>Jefferson High School operates on multiple bell schedules. The regular weekly rotation runs Flex / Advisory days on Monday, Tuesday, Thursday, and Friday, and Colab days on Wednesday. Special schedules apply for rallies, finals, minimum days, and Foods Day events.</p><h3>Flex / Advisory Days (M / T / Th / F)</h3><table><colgroup><col style=\"width:60%\"><col style=\"width:40%\"></colgroup><thead><tr><th>Period</th><th>Time</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st Period</td><td>8:30 - 9:51</td></tr><tr><td>Brunch</td><td>9:51 - 10:06</td></tr><tr><td>2nd Period</td><td>10:11 - 11:32</td></tr><tr><td>Flex / Advisory</td><td>11:37 - 12:08</td></tr><tr><td>Lunch</td><td>12:08 - 12:38</td></tr><tr><td>3rd Period</td><td>12:43 - 2:04</td></tr><tr><td>4th Period</td><td>2:09 - 3:30</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Colab Days (Wednesdays)</h3><table><colgroup><col style=\"width:60%\"><col style=\"width:40%\"></colgroup><thead><tr><th>Period</th><th>Time</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st Period</td><td>8:30 - 9:49</td></tr><tr><td>Brunch</td><td>9:49 - 10:04</td></tr><tr><td>2nd Period</td><td>10:09 - 11:28</td></tr><tr><td>Lunch</td><td>11:28 - 11:58</td></tr><tr><td>3rd Period</td><td>12:03 - 1:22</td></tr><tr><td>4th Period</td><td>1:27 - 2:46</td></tr><tr><td>Collab</td><td>2:55 - 3:45</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Rally Schedule</h3><table><colgroup><col style=\"width:60%\"><col style=\"width:40%\"></colgroup><thead><tr><th>Period</th><th>Time</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st Period</td><td>8:30 - 9:45</td></tr><tr><td>Brunch</td><td>9:45 - 10:00</td></tr><tr><td>2nd Period</td><td>10:05 - 11:20</td></tr><tr><td>All staff / students walk down to GYM</td><td>11:20 - 11:25</td></tr><tr><td>Rally</td><td>11:25 - 12:20</td></tr><tr><td>Lunch</td><td>12:20 - 12:50</td></tr><tr><td>3rd Period</td><td>12:55 - 2:10</td></tr><tr><td>4th Period</td><td>2:15 - 3:30</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Finals Schedule</h3><table><colgroup><col style=\"width:60%\"><col style=\"width:40%\"></colgroup><thead><tr><th>Period</th><th>Time</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st / 3rd</td><td>8:30 - 10:50</td></tr><tr><td>Brunch</td><td>10:50 - 11:20</td></tr><tr><td>2nd / 4th</td><td>11:25 - 1:45</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Minimum Day Schedule</h3><table><colgroup><col style=\"width:60%\"><col style=\"width:40%\"></colgroup><thead><tr><th>Period</th><th>Time</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Advisory</td><td>8:30 - 9:00</td></tr><tr><td>1st Period</td><td>9:05 - 9:55</td></tr><tr><td>2nd Period</td><td>10:00 - 10:50</td></tr><tr><td>Brunch</td><td>10:50 - 11:10</td></tr><tr><td>3rd Period</td><td>11:15 - 12:05</td></tr><tr><td>4th Period</td><td>12:10 - 1:00</td></tr></tbody></table><h3>Foods Day Schedule</h3><table><colgroup><col style=\"width:60%\"><col style=\"width:40%\"></colgroup><thead><tr><th>Period</th><th>Time</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st Period</td><td>8:30 - 9:51</td></tr><tr><td>2nd Period</td><td>9:56 - 11:17</td></tr><tr><td>Flex / Advisory</td><td>11:22 - 11:53</td></tr><tr><td>Lunch</td><td>11:53 - 12:38</td></tr><tr><td>3rd Period</td><td>12:43 - 2:04</td></tr><tr><td>4th Period</td><td>2:09 - 3:30</td></tr></tbody></table>",
